  <h2>⚔️ The Founding — Velious Era, Tunare Server</h2>
  <p>The Order of the Eternal Moon was forged in the frozen crucible of the Velious era on the Tunare server of EverQuest. In a time when the continent of Velious was newly discovered and the great dragons of the Ring of Scale and the Claws of Veeshan waged their eternal war, a band of adventurers united under a common banner.</p>
  <p>Led by visionaries who understood that strength came not from individual power but from unity of purpose, the Order carved its name into the annals of Tunare's history. While the great powers — Divine Crusade, Talisman, Stars, and Cynosure — dominated the endgame, the Order of the Eternal Moon held its ground as a respected force in the raiding scene.</p>

  <div class="lore-quote">
    "In Velious I was in Order of the Eternal Moon with my cousin Drudgee (Iksar Monk). I remember DC, Talisman, Stars, Tide, and Cynosure. Cool to see others from Tunare here!"
    <br><br>
    <span style="color:var(--text-muted);">— Annebell, Halfling Druid, original OotEM member on Tunare</span>
  </div>

  <h2>❄️ The Velious Campaigns</h2>
  <p>The Order stood shoulder to shoulder in the frozen wastes, taking on the challenges that Velious presented:</p>
  
