  <h2>🌙 Rebirth — EverQuest Legends 2026</h2>
  <p>Decades later, the call of Norrath grows strong once more. With the launch of EverQuest Legends on July 28, 2026 — a faithful reimagining of the 1999 classic — the Order of the Eternal Moon rises again on the <strong>Rivervale</strong> server. The same spirit, the same values, reborn for a new age.</p>
  <p>EverQuest Legends brings back the classic art style, MIDI music, and zones of 1999 while introducing modern quality-of-life features: multiclassing, enhanced UI, smaller group sizes, and a solo-friendly world. For returning veterans and new adventurers alike, it's the perfect time to rally under the moon.</p>

  <h2>📜 Our Charter</h2>
  <p>The Order of the Eternal Moon is built on principles that transcend any single game or era:</p>
  <ul style="color:var(--text-secondary);list-style:none;padding:0;">
    <li style="padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">✦ <strong>Unity</strong> — We rise together, we fall together. No member left behind.</li>
    <li style="padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">✦ <strong>Honor</strong> — Fair loot distribution through our transparent DKP system.</li>
    <li style="padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">✦ <strong>Perseverance</strong> — From Velious to Legends, we endure.</li>
    <li style="padding:8px 0;">✦ <strong>Community</strong> — Veterans and newcomers alike are welcome under the moon.</li>
  </ul>

  <div style="text-align:center;margin:3rem 0;padding:2rem;background:var(--bg-secondary);border-radius:12px;border:1px solid var(--border);">
    <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--accent);font-style:italic;">"The moon watches over all who walk in its light.<br>Once sworn, always bound. The Order endures."</p>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:0.5rem;">— Guild Motto of the Order of the Eternal Moon</p>
  </div>
